{"tid":691794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[豬閪伯] Facebook承認與華為等中國科技公司分享數據","createTime":"2018-06-06T05:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T06:17:37.000Z","uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1f6eb04126ede2fe2b8cdb16adc1198613d15f04","tid":691794,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:11:16.000Z","msg":"《紐約時報》報道，Facebook與至少四家中國科技公司有數據共享協議，而該協議可追溯至2010年。根據協議內容，Facebook允許華為、聯想、廣東歐珀移動通信和TCL集團訪問設備用戶及其朋友的詳細信息。但Facebook表示，可能於本周結束與華為的協議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/131110_043ab0ec0976b0963523d742dc22973c.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F131110_043ab0ec0976b0963523d742dc22973c.PNG&h=2e594847&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1528251993476&amp;issue=20180606\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1528251993476%26issue%3D20180606&d=vhjfVoIsUf8uppYeFv%2B2Icn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=44918092\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1528251993476%26issue%3D20180606&h=efef9e78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1528251993476&amp;issue=20180606</a>"},{"pid":"665a29aa6cc6eb75df56b67de7ef1fddf8cf49ca","tid":691794,"uid":28845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T05:14:32.000Z","msg":"molamola"},{"pid":"041d7eba566336edd53f5bf5c5a9720fe8f546f9","tid":691794,"uid":109923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T06:02:49.000Z","msg":"成日奶共 然而中共冇撚理過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成隻毒撚做兵咁款"},{"pid":"af1a8d8951246bc9b5ffb7409d1f3e12bd85a781","tid":691794,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"041d7eba566336edd53f5bf5c5a9720fe8f546f9","tid":691794,"u